nodes.text: Faye was a male doctor who worked on biological research for Czerka Corporation at their CZ-198 research facility. Faye stole his coworker Brendan Hillin's warra nut cookies from the employee refrigeration unit and left a hologram of himself, mouth full of cookies, in its place. Hillin was furious, and filed a formal complaint calling for Faye's dismissal as a result.
